headline: Q4 Rundown: Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) Vs Other Specialized Consumer Services Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at specialized consumer services stocks, starting with Pool (NASDAQ:POOL).
